// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2598 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 4ffeaee6-e6c0-5ad4-82b0-c87e1bd907ce

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
